    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L straight-six, an engine renowned for its six individual throttle bodies and high-revving valvetrain. This example is mechanically superlative, with a meticulously maintained double-VANOS system and a documented subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity. Power is managed via a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock, providing tactile engagement and precise torque distribution. The exterior retains its factory paint depth with no signs of clear coat failure or road rash, while the interior remains in a preserved state with no bolster wear. This is a zero-leak, high-compression unit optimized for the purist who demands peak atmospheric performance and analog feedback.",
